Package pl.polsl.michal.urbanek.hotelmanagementsystem.controller

Class RoomController

  • java.lang.Object
    • pl.polsl.michal.urbanek.hotelmanagementsystem.controller.RoomController
  • public class RoomController
extends Object
    Controller class dealing with the processing of room data. It provides for catching exceptions and is responsible for passing the appropriate data to the model and view.
